# GUI Time Zone Clock

A Python-based GUI clock that displays four U.S time zone:
PST, MST, CST, and EST.

## Scope
- Debian-based Linux systems only
- GUI desktop environment required
- Manual launch only (no auto-start)

## Purpose
This project is used to practice Devops fundamentals such as version control, packaging decisions,
and deployment to multiple machines.

## Requirements
- Debian-based Linux (Ubuntu, Debian, etc.)
- Python 3.10+
- python3-tk (Tkinter GUI support)

## Install dependencies:

```bash
sudo apt update
sudo apt install python3 python3-tk
